---
// Software subscription recommendations for laptop users
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="Software Subscriptions for Laptop Users | LaptopVette"
    description="Recommended software subscriptions for laptop users, including writing tools, productivity apps, and creative services."
    path="/software-subscriptions"
    type="article"
  />
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container nav-container">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Laptop<span>Vette</span></a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="article-container">
    <header class="article-header">
      <span class="category-tag">Subscriptions</span>
      <h1>Best Software Subscriptions for Laptop Users</h1>
      <p class="byline">Top yearly and monthly services that support productivity, creativity, and everyday laptop work.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="summary-section">
      <h2>Recommended Subscription Categories</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Office suites:</strong> Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace support documents, spreadsheets, and presentations.</li>
        <li><strong>Writing aids:</strong> Grammarly, ProWritingAid, and similar services help users write better and catch mistakes.</li>
        <li><strong>Creative tools:</strong> Canva, Adobe Express, and design platforms support productivity and content creation.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="detail-section">
      <h2>Why Subscription Software Converts Well</h2>
      <p>Software subscriptions provide ongoing value for laptop users through upgrades, cloud access, and productivity features. Many plans also offer family packages and cross-device syncing for continued use.</p>
      <p>Linking from laptop buying guides to productivity and creative software is a strong way to extend value beyond the initial hardware purchase.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <a href="/back-to-school-laptops" class="btn btn-primary">Return to Laptop Buying Guides</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #f8fafc; color: #0f172a; line-height: 1.85; }
  .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .navbar { background: #ffffff; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px 0; }
  .logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; color: #0f172a; }
  .logo span { color: #b91c1c; }
  .article-container { max-width: 1064px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 40px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; }
  .category-tag { color: #b91c1c; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 11px; }
  h1 { font-size: 34px; margin: 15px 0; }
  .byline { color: #475569; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; }
  h2 { margin: 56px 0 22px 0; font-size: 22px; color: #1e1b4b; font-weight: 700; border-left: 4px solid #b91c1c; padding-left: 15px; }
  .summary-section, .detail-section { margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .summary-section ul, .detail-section ul { margin: 15px 0 0 20px; color: #334155; }
  .summary-section li, .detail-section li { margin-bottom: 18px; font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.8; }
  .summary-section p, .detail-section p { margin-bottom: 1.4em; line-height: 1.85; text-align: justify; color: #334155; }
  .btn-primary { display: inline-block; background: #b91c1c; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #991b1b; }
</style>